<h1>Time Card</h1>

 <table>
<TR><TH>Employee<TH>Month<TH>Payday<TH>Exception<TH>Dates</TR>
<TR><TD rowspan=4> <form-variable name=employee options=users> </form-variable>
    <TD rowspan=4> <form-variable name=paymonth options="01 02 03 04 05 06 07 08 09 10 11 12">&month; </form-variable>
    <TD rowspan=4> <form-variable name=payday options="15 30">&day; </form-variable>

<TD> Sick Days  <TD> <form-variable name=sick> </form-variable> </TR>
<TR><TD> Personal Holidays  <TD> <form-variable name=holiday> </form-variable>
</TR>
<TR><TD> Vacation Days  <TD> <form-variable name=vacation> </form-variable>
</TR>
<TR><TD> Other Days  <TD> <form-variable name=other> </form-variable> </TR>
</table>

<p>
Time cards for regular employees ("Exempt Personnel") are reported by
exception. If you did not miss any workdays this pay period, leave the dates
above blank and click on the Process button. Otherwise enter the dates missed
in the appropriate boxes and then click Process.
